==发行==
2015年9月12日在[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]上首映。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/watch-the-trailer-for-tiffs-first-person-sci-fi-actioner-hardcore-starring-sharlto-copley-20150914 |title=Watch The Trailer For TIFF's First-Person Sci-Fi Actioner |publisher=Blogs.indiewire.com |date= |accessdate=2015-09-16 |archive-date=2015-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916215055/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/watch-the-trailer-for-tiffs-first-person-sci-fi-actioner-hardcore-starring-sharlto-copley-20150914 |dead-url=no }}</ref>STX娱乐经过竞争以1千万美元取得了影片的全球发行权，成为该公司首部从影展上获得发行权的电影<ref name="DeadlineTIFF"></ref>。

